- [P1] Automation continues after package load failure - app.js:371-390  
  `runAutomation()` awaits `loadFolderFromServer(pkg)` but the callee returns normally for “no supported files” and catches load errors, so automation can continue against a previously auto-loaded package. Make `loadFolderFromServer` return success/throw on failure, then abort translate/save unless the requested package actually loaded.

- [P1] Editing an existing link bypasses URL safety validation - app.js:8205-8219  
